  "description": "NYC Department of Sanitation mandatory-containerization rollout. Cohort 1 (pilot): lower-Manhattan community districts MN 01-09, effective 2023-07-01. Cohort 2 (citywide residential 1-9-unit buildings): all other standard community districts, effective 2024-11-12. High-number districts (airports, parks, cemeteries, Rikers Island — CDs with district number >= 20) and 'Unspecified' geocoding-failure districts are not part of either cohort and serve as never-treated controls for the staggered DiD.",
